"a.残忍的；严酷的 【英】 adj.残忍的(savage, violent)；严酷的(very harsh and rigorous) 【同】 派生词: brutality (n.残酷，兽行) adj. (态度或语言)野蛮残忍的, 粗暴无礼的 = savage = violent; (天气)严酷的 = harsh = rigorous 【例】the brutal truth 残酷的事实 a brutal winter 严冬 【记】brut野兽－野蛮残忍的. 参: brutality(n 残酷, 兽行) 【记】brute畜生 + al；音：捕虏头，捕获俘虏了一头野兽 brutal (adj.)  mid-15c., in reference to the nature of animals, from Latin brutus (see brute (adj.)) + -al (1). Of persons, ""fierce,"" 1640s. Related: Brutally."
